29dce70b12c72e02f30778294954fe","tid":1324452,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"暫緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c638800aa1bcc189ff2c4211e46f68b9de6a41","tid":1324452,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n除左做文宣本身之外，仲可以提供答案，用黎回應藍絲親戚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6183c09fe5712159c0783d73cf83b080692d9ed","tid":1324452,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"《<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>反大灣區一國一制融合 !!!</ins></span></strong>》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由小處到大局，逃犯條例的真面目。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉聰已鋪路，香港警隊將歸大灣區管！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1292683/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1292683/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港點解會變軍政府？詳細解說</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1296899/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1296899/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港3年內引進「信用評分系統」(2018年開始計)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298473/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298473/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智慧(監控)燈柱關注組 持續更新 (有詳細資料+公開信) </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1310657/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1310657/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0caa43c664526b2aa2479172827d813f164bc4f0","tid":1324452,"uid":270511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"我好想知道商業區點樣非法傾倒建築廢物?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938c48beeb5002e11a3562c2fbbfad2b96b72bf2","tid":1324452,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"暫你老母暫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7c69a3561193dcb566ec4e12777519285fc823","tid":1324452,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n監控燈柱 5G small-cell<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c2def6822b72ccd41bcd267b54023ffd818186b","tid":1324452,"uid":261773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"等我幫大家將中文翻譯做中文啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;不會傳送到第三方作人臉識別應用&quot; = in-house 自己做<br />\n<br />\n&quot;燈柱系統無人臉識別功能&quot; = 燈柱系統無人臉識別功能，但會將影像輸出到外置system做人臉識別<br />\n<br />\n其實一般machine learning 都係用外置server 黎 train model同run model, client 機好少會run model (新式係edge行除外，但政府咁outdate 唔識玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），所以佢無講大話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22babd89a68ee69f368b9bfb2053f677733737c0","tid":1324452,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫不啟用</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc053032a503143a6fd14789f7101388cade4bf8","tid":1324452,"uid":193100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T23:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\